---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="MelisaRockStone Music">

  <!-- HERO BANNER GOES HERE -->
  <div class="hero-banner">
    <img
      src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}hero.jpg`}
      alt="Melisa Rockstone live performance"
    />
  </div>

  <section class="card">
    <h1 style="margin:0 0 8px;">MelisaRockStone Music</h1>
    <p style="margin:0;opacity:.92;">
      Gritty blues-rooted rock with Florida heat and bayou soul.
    </p>


    <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:14px;">
     <a class="button" href="events">Events</a>
<a class="button" href="merch">Merch</a>
      <a class="button" href="mailto:Melisarockstone@gmail.com">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="card" style="margin-top:18px;">
    <h2 style="margin:0 0 10px;">Bio</h2>
    <p style="margin:0;opacity:.92;max-width:78ch;">
      I create blues-driven rock formed through real life — through hard seasons, rebuilding, and the kind of transformation that reshapes your character from the inside out.

Born and raised in Plant City, Florida, I carry the grit, rhythm, and backbone of the South into every note I write.

I’m a self-producing artist. Guitar, vocals, flute, and modern production tools all stay in my hands so the music remains honest and unfiltered.

Recording work has taken place in Florida and Morocco — environments that continue to shape the texture and direction of what I create.

This isn’t music built for noise.

It’s music built to steady you.

New releases, live performances, and deeper projects are underway.

If the sound resonates, you’re invited to follow the journey.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
